==歷史==
13號堪薩斯州州道曾為連結曼哈頓至[[埃爾多拉多_(堪薩斯州)|埃爾多拉多]]之間的公路，行經距離相當地長。1965年，{{le|177號堪薩斯州州道|K-177 (Kansas highway)}}取代此公路的部分路段。此公路由於因大壩建設而產生出塔特爾溪湖之前，曾經是塔特爾溪西岸（賴利縣東邊縣界）的基準線<ref>{{cite map |url= http://www.ksdot.org/Assets/wwwksdotorg/bureaus/burTransPlan/maps/HistoricStateMaps/1961Mapside.pdf |format= PDF |publisher= Kansas State Highway Commission |title= Official Kansas Highway Map |year= 1961 |scale= Scale not given |cartography= KSHC |section= B10–C10 |accessdate= 2015-03-02 |archive-date= 2014-07-28 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140728123249/http://ksdot.org/Assets/wwwksdotorg/bureaus/burTransPlan/maps/HistoricStateMaps/1961Mapside.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

